  - assign-zero-domain-guard: Fused altitude store and "<= 0" terminal-error branch through F lg.
  - proc-call-lowering: Compiled call to rule close_range as ПП/В/О subroutine.
  - single-use-rule-inline: Inlined single-use rule dive at line 45.
  - preloaded-constant: Used preloaded Rb for constant -10.
  - proc-call-lowering: Compiled call to rule __param_sibling_proc_0 as ПП/В/О subroutine.
  - x-param-proc-call: Passed __param_sibling_delta_0 to rule __param_sibling_proc_0 through X at line 46.
