  - shared-call-tail: Shared 3 call+jump tail sequences.
  - store-recall-peephole: Dropped 1 redundant П->X immediately after X->П to the same register.
  - jump-to-next-threading: Removed 1 unconditional branch to the immediately following label.
  - jump-thread: Threaded 1 jump(s) through trampoline labels to the final target. (+Threaded 6 jump(s) through trampoline labels to the final target.)
  - dead-store-elimination: Removed 2 store(s) to register(s) never read before the next assignment.
  - dead-code-after-halt: Removed 3 unreachable op(s) from the entry CFG.
  - generated-setup-program: Generated optimized setup program for .
  - setup-duplicate-preload-store-reuse: Loaded setup constant 0 once and stored it into R3, R1, R2.
