  - single-use-rule-inline: Inlined single-use rule try_move at line 86.
  - x-param-proc-entry: Compiled rule go to consume dir directly from X.
  - show-read-stake-sin-lowering: Reused displayed stake as the stack stake for int(stake * (1 + sin(fight_entry))).
  - tail-call-lowering: Replaced 5 subroutine tail operations with direct jump continuation.
  - store-recall-peephole: Dropped 4 redundant П->X immediately after X->П to the same register.
  - jump-thread: Threaded 6 jump(s) through trampoline labels to the final target.
  - dead-store-elimination: Removed 1 store(s) to register(s) never read before the next assignment.
  - dead-code-after-halt: Removed 1 unreachable op(s) from the entry CFG.
