  - dark-entry-layout: Pointed 2 branch(es) at an executable suffix through a proven dark-entry formal address (beyond the 104-cell window).
  - generated-setup-program: Generated optimized setup program for walls_1, walls_2, walls_3, caches.
  - setup-duplicate-preload-store-reuse: Loaded setup constant 0 once and stored it into Re, R9, Rc, R8.
